<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<section class="home-page">
  <div class="intro">
    <h1 class="home-page-title">Welcome to MotoMeter</h1>
    <p class="sub-title">- a dirtbike maintenance tracking utility.</p>
    <div class="intro-questions">
      <p>
        Tired of using post-its, notepads or dry-erase boards to keep track of
        your bike's service requirements?
      </p>
      <p>Does your bike have an hourmeter?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-bullets">
      <i class="fas fa-motorcycle animate-color"></i>
      <p>Create a profile for every dirtbike you own/maintain.</p>

      <i class="fas fa-tools animate-color"></i>
      <p>Create maintenance tasks and set the service interval.</p>

      <i class="fas fa-stopwatch animate-color"></i>
      <p>
        After each ride enter the new hourmeter reading to update the remaining
        time until service is due for each task.
      </p>

      <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list animate-color"></i>
      <p>
        Notes section to record torques, specifications, maintenance steps, and
        whatever else you have scribbled down in the garage.
      </p>

      <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check animate-color"></i>
      <p>Optional pre-ride inspection checklist.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-cta">
      <div class="intro-reg">
        <a href="/register" class="link">Sign Up</a> to get started.
      </div>
      <div class="intro-android"><span>Android app on</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
